The paper deals with computer vision and 3D reconstruction, which are both subfields of computer science. The focus is on object detection datasets, which falls under computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves optimization and camera viewpoint estimation, which are related to graphics (cs.GR) and robotics (cs.RO), respectively. The proposed algorithm also involves assumptions and sampling, which are related to machine learning (cs.AI) and statistical learning (cs.LG).
